-- Colorado Suspect Held on First Degree Murder Suspicion
-- B y   J e f f   K a s s
-- 2012-07-23T15:52:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-23/colorado-shooting-suspect-appears-in-court-charges-read.html
James Holmes, suspected in the
shooting deaths of 12 people at an Aurora, Colorado movie
theater, appeared for a short initial hearing today in state
court in Centennial. He was advised of his rights, that he
is suspected of first degree murder, and ordered to return to
court on July 30 for the filing of formal charges.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David E. Rovella in  New York  at 
